176 A.3d 224 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. KELVIN REYES, A/K/A KEVIN REYES, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-421 September Term 2017

079678 December 8, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003397-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
